{
  "text": "International Journal of Dentistry Dorland's Illustrated Medical Dictionary defines syndrome as \"A set of symptoms that occur together; the sum of signs of any morbid state; a symptom complex. In genetics, a pattern of multiple malformations thought to be pathogenetically related\" [CITATION_1] .",
